description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Full Body Stretching Exercises - Stretching For Beginners!' from the channel Jessica Valant.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 15 Minute Full Body Stretching Exercises is perfect for beginners or anyone wanting a great full body stretching workout! This stretching for beginners workout focuses on breathing, flexibility exercises and movement to help with joint mobility, posture and more. Created by a physical therapist, this stretching workout is gentle enough to do every day!
